	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64146693">The entire legal intent of copyright is to assure the availability of existing works and future creative works from a creator as a benefit to society.  If content is not available at all, then it should not have copyright protection.  Period. Too expensive is not a legal excuse, but nothing in this age should be unavailable.</div>
	</div>

