<span class="ind"></span><a id="reply_link_64146783" class="btn link" href="//yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23188513&amp;op=Reply&amp;threshold=1&amp;commentsort=0&amp;mode=thread&amp;pid=64146783" onclick="D2.replyTo(64146783); return false;">Reply to This</a> 	<a href="#" class="comment_share_toggle btn link">Share</a>
	<div class="comment_share sharethis-0 hide"><span class="au"></span>
		<a class="t slashpop" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=No surprise...%20by%20Travelsonic%20%40slashdot%20https://yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23188513&cid=64146783" target="_blank">twitter</a>
		<a class="f slashpop" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23188513&cid=64146783" target="_blank">facebook</a>
		<a class="g" href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=https://yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23188513&cid=64146783" onclick="javascript:window.open(this.href,'', 'menubar=no,toolbar=no,resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,height=600,width=600');return false;"><img src="https://www.gstatic.com/images/icons/gplus-16.png" alt="Share on Google+"/></a>


	</div>
 <span class="ind"></span><a id="reply_link_64146783" title="Flag this comment as Inappropriate" class="ui-icon flag fright" href="//yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23188513&amp;op=flag&amp;threshold=1&amp;commentsort=0&amp;mode=thread&amp;pid=64146783" onclick="return false;">Flag as Inappropriate</a>
